Author: alchademy
Text: Ask yourself what’s more of a loss: A. Today’s food intake, something that doesn’t really matter in the long run. Everybody’s got their bad days, you can’t gain actual fat from one day of eating. or B. A 3 year clean streak that you’ve worked so hard to reach.
